platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Limbo is a gripping blend of stark, haunting landscapes, bizarre characters, and unsettling sounds. With clever puzzle design, an intriguing narrative, and an excellent touch-screen control system, it’s as rewarding to play as it is interesting to look at and listen to.

Limbo is a gripping blend of stark, haunting landscapes, bizarre characters and unsettling sounds. With clever puzzle design, an intriguing narrative and an excellent touch-screen control system, it’s as rewarding to play as it is interesting to look at and listen to.

Parcourez ces mondes de brume à la merci des éléments et des personnages mystérieux de la forêt. Commandes intuitives et histoire captivante font de ce jeu exceptionnel une aventure où tous vos sens sont mis à l’épreuve.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Dark, haunting, beautiful. This'll stay with you long after it's over.
